Package org.rabbittownsoftware.jtiled

package org.rabbittownsoftware.jtiled
  • Class
    Description
    TiledLayer
    Represents a single tile layer inside a Tiled map (.tmx file).
    TiledMap
    Represents a parsed Tiled map (.tmx) containing layers, tilesets, and objects.
    TiledMap.Builder
    Builder for constructing immutable TiledMap instances.
    TiledObject
    Represents an individual object defined in a Tiled map's object layer.
    TiledParser
    TiledParser handles reading and parsing TMX map files exported from the Tiled map editor.
    TiledTileset
    Represents a tileset definition in a Tiled map (.tmx or .tsx).
